    "definition": "The mask is authority. I am the means by which the arcana reveals all things — the protagonist, the hero. When the mask is on, I am the final word. Authority translates to ruthlessness when the hard thing needs doing — but the whole team knows what must be done and does it. I am not the sole bearer of will; I am the focal point of shared will.",
